{"type":null,"faqId":40456,"title":"Wi-Fi中继、Wi-Fi扩展和智联有什么区别？应该如何选择？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.15763889in;margin-left:0.15763889in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:24pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>Wi-Fi中继、Wi-Fi扩展和智联的区别如下：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span>当使用Wi-Fi中继时，路由器将工作在桥接模式下。路由器的下挂设备将直接从主路由器获取IP地址上网。主从两台路由器的下挂设备都在一个子网里，可以相互访问。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span>当使用Wi-Fi扩展时，路由器将工作在路由器模式下。它可以进行拨号，并为它的下挂设备分配IP地址。主从两台路由器的下挂设备将分别在两个子网里，不可以相互访问。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span>智联的使用条件必须是两台路由器均支持华为智联功能。它分为有线直连和Hi按键无线连接。在有线直连的情况下，将工作在路由器模式，上网方式为DHCP；在Hi按键无线连接的情况下即为Wi-Fi中继。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>您可以根据不同的使用场景选择合适的互联方式：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span class=\"s2\">使用场景一：</span><span>家中已有一台无线路由器能正常上网的情况下，首选Wi-Fi中继方式，其次，选用Wi-Fi扩展的DHCP上网方式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span class=\"s2\">使用场景二</span><span>：家中已有一台无线路由器工作在桥接模式，需要进行Wi-Fi扩展并且拨号上网时，则需要选择Wi-Fi扩展的PPPoE拨号上网方式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span class=\"s2\">使用场景三：</span><span>如果两台路由器都支持华为智联，则使用智联互联。</span>\n</p>\n<br>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5803","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441768490000,"seriesProductName":"WS832-10","visitedTimes":29,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}